data.eml:eml: A new species of Nuuanu (Crustacea, Amphipoda, Nuuanuidae) from a Caribbean coral reef with identification keys to males and females of Nuuanu species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Ortiz, Manuel, Winfield, Ignacio (2017): A new species of Nuuanu (Crustacea, Amphipoda, Nuuanuidae) from a Caribbean coral reef with identification keys to males and females of Nuuanu species. Zootaxa 4294 (2): 197-208, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4294.2.4
